title: (Tues Full Show) Should Ray Connect With Barbara Corcoran After She Liked His Business Idea? + Bobby's Exciting Football Interview News + Are We Powerball Winners?
itunes:title: (Tues Full Show) Should Ray Connect With Barbara Corcoran After She Liked His Business Idea? + Bobby's Exciting Football Interview News + Are We Powerball Winners?
description:
Last week we had Shark Tank's Barbara Corcoran on the show and when Ray pitched his business idea to her, she actually said she would invest in it! Now Ray wants to know if he should reach back out to her and try to make this actually happen... Plus, Bobby recently emailed an NFL team asking if he could interview their owner for the 25 Whistles podcast. He shares their exciting response! Then, we once again bought lottery tickets to try and win big in the Powerball. Find out if we won anything! 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
